    "This learning process is facilitated through four primary techniques: supervised, unsupervised, semi-supervised, and reinforcement learning (Jha et al. 2021), each defining a unique training approach.",
    "Interestingly, from the 52 related works found, only one study focused on reinforcement learning; this will be discussed in Sect. 3.",
    "In short, reinforcement learning comprises algorithm learning, which is achieved by being given an observation of a particular activity rather than a label itself.",
